{"tid":1270731,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(伊朗) 批准華客免簽證入境　分析︰避免遊客受美懲罰","createTime":"2019-07-01T02:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T12:15:43.000Z","uid":48958,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"365908af576f451b8fd02ada9e49069aacb237c9","tid":1270731,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"伊朗文化遺產、手工藝和旅遊組織副主任泰穆里（Vali Teymouri）上周六（6月29日）宣布，內閣已批准對中國遊客實行免簽證入境政策，中國遊客前往伊朗不再需要簽證，惟伊朗遊客前往中國仍需簽證。伊朗傳媒報道，伊朗馬漢航空已確認收到消息，但相關細則和落實時間尚未公布。 <br />\n<br />\n據報道，美國政府去年曾警告，遊客到訪某些國家，特別是伊朗後，入境美國時可能會受到限制。對此，伊朗總統魯哈尼早前命令內政部長法茲利，規定在到訪伊朗的外國人護照上不再蓋簽證章，也不做任何標記。報道分析，有關決定有利於鼓勵外國人不必擔心美國的懲罰，前往伊朗旅行。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190701/mobile/bkn-20190701071620969-0701_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190701%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190701071620969-0701_00912_001.html&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5a7ee7a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190701/mobile/bkn-20190701071620969-0701_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6e7e82bf32b9569920ae628f5e241d1ab614356","tid":1270731,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/437541/Iran-waives-visa-for-Chinese-tourists\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tehrantimes.com%2Fnews%2F437541%2FIran-waives-visa-for-Chinese-tourists&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=483c3731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/437541/Iran-waives-visa-for-Chinese-tourists</a>"},{"pid":"b686a546354fca541e77904fe389c0ce1c97fa56","tid":1270731,"uid":109933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"包唔包香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}